content: Hello everyone, welcome to this course of Inteliball.
In the module 6 of this course, we will learn how we can visualize our findings during the
analysis for a better understanding of the data.
The objective is to familiarize you with various plots that are used for different set
of data such as bar plot, a scatter plot, a histogram, etc. for data that are of the
type categorical, ordinal or continuous in nature.
